M834 80h400000v40h-400000z"></path></svg></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height: 0.1328em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style="top: -3.23em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height: 3em;"></span><span class="frac-line" style="border-bottom-width: 0.04em;"></span></span><span style="top: -3.677em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height: 3em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">VIX</span></span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height: 0.93em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mclose nulldelimiter"></span></span></span></span></span></span>
<p data-start="629" data-end="634">Then:</p>
<ul data-start="635" data-end="712">
<li data-section-id="psv1pw" data-start="635" data-end="673">
<p data-start="637" data-end="673">Upper Range = Spot + Expected Move</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="138n3pp" data-start="674" data-end="712">
<p data-start="676" data-end="712">Lower Range = Spot – Expected Move</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="714" data-end="784">👉 This gives a <strong data-start="730" data-end="753">1-day implied range</strong> (assuming normal distribution)</p>
<hr data-start="786" data-end="789">
<h2 data-section-id="1m441cy" data-start="791" data-end="815">🚀 Where You Left Off</h2>
<p data-start="817" data-end="827">You asked:</p>
<blockquote data-start="828" data-end="862">
<p data-start="830" data-end="862">“Code run ho gaya… ab kya karu?”</p>
</blockquote>
<p data-start="864" data-end="961">So here’s the <strong data-start="878" data-end="900">next steps roadmap</strong> (this is what actually makes it a <em data-start="935" data-end="944">project</em>, not just code):</p>
<hr data-start="963" data-end="966">
<h2 data-section-id="13v1m2q" data-start="968" data-end="1008">🧩 Step 1: Turn It Into a Usable Tool</h2>
<p data-start="1010" data-end="1043">You need a UI layer. Two options:</p>
<h3 data-section-id="18ak1u9" data-start="1045" data-end="1082">Option A (Fastest): Streamlit App</h3>
<ul data-start="1083" data-end="1261">
<li data-section-id="16dghws" data-start="1083" data-end="1165">
<p data-start="1085" data-end="1165">Convert your <code data-start="1098" data-end="1106">app.py</code> into a <strong data-start="1114" data-end="1165"><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Streamlit</span></span> dashboard</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="kb46t4" data-start="1166" data-end="1261">
<p data-start="1168" data-end="1172">Add:</p>
<ul data-start="1175" data-end="1261">
<li data-section-id="1k6w5qp" data-start="1175" data-end="1194">
<p data-start="1177" data-end="1194">Input: Spot price</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1cndhwj" data-start="1197" data-end="1209">
<p data-start="1199" data-end="1209">Input: VIX</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="7x3zoy" data-start="1212" data-end="1227">
<p data-start="1214" data-end="1227">Output: Range</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1a83763" data-start="1230" data-end="1261">
<p data-start="1232" data-end="1261">Optional: Strategy suggestion</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1263" data-end="1303">👉 This is BEST for your internship/demo</p>
<hr data-start="1305" data-end="1308">
<h2 data-section-id="18uyov2" data-start="1310" data-end="1362">📊 Step 2: Add Strategy Layer (THIS IS YOUR EDGE)</h2>
<p data-start="1364" data-end="1387">Now link it to options:</p>
<h3 data-section-id="1h7lyyc" data-start="1389" data-end="1414">Short Strangle Logic:</h3>
<ul data-start="1415" data-end="1471">
<li data-section-id="767ipg" data-start="1415" data-end="1443">
<p data-start="1417" data-end="1443">Sell Call at Upper Range</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="5hacg6" data-start="1444" data-end="1471">
<p data-start="1446" data-end="1471">Sell Put at Lower Range</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1473" data-end="1496">BUT ⚠️ your assumption:</p>
<blockquote data-start="1497" data-end="1525">
<p data-start="1499" data-end="1525">“No loss” ❌ — <strong data-start="1513" data-end="1525">not true</strong></p>
</blockquote>
<h3 data-section-id="1dow002" data-start="1527" data-end="1539">Reality:</h3>
<ul data-start="1540" data-end="1654">
<li data-section-id="1ld9r0g" data-start="1540" data-end="1592">
<p data-start="1542" data-end="1561">You profit only if:</p>
<ul data-start="1564" data-end="1592">
<li data-section-id="65lw37" data-start="1564" data-end="1592">
<p data-start="1566" data-end="1592">Price stays within range</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
<li data-section-id="tgwmbe" data-start="1593" data-end="1654">
<p data-start="1595" data-end="1607">You lose if:</p>
<ul data-start="1610" data-end="1654">
<li data-section-id="1q5hvzy" data-start="1610" data-end="1654">
<p data-start="1612" data-end="1654">Big move beyond expected range (fat tails)</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1656" data-end="1715">👉 VIX gives <strong data-start="1669" data-end="1715">expected volatility, not guaranteed bounds</strong></p>
<hr data-start="1717" data-end="1720">
<h2 data-section-id="17i2y7d" data-start="1722" data-end="1782">⚠️ Critical Improvement (Very Important for Your Project)</h2>
<p data-start="1784" data-end="1822">Right now your model is <strong data-start="1808" data-end="1821">too naive</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="1824" data-end="1845">Upgrade it like this:</p>
<h3 data-section-id="pf9yv6" data-start="1847" data-end="1875">🔹 Add Confidence Levels</h3>
<p data-start="1876" data-end="1899">Instead of 1 range, do:</p>
<ul data-start="1900" data-end="1921">
<li data-section-id="ioez2o" data-start="1900" data-end="1910">
<p data-start="1902" data-end="1910">1σ (68%)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="5jnh01" data-start="1911" data-end="1921">
<p data-start="1913" data-end="1921">2σ (95%)</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h3 data-section-id="kt8d4r" data-start="1923" data-end="1934">🔹 Use:</h3>
<span class="katex-display" style=""><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="block"><semantics><mrow><mtext>Range</mtext><mo>=</mo><mtext>Spot</mtext><mo>×</mo><mtext>VIX</mtext><mo>×</mo><msqrt><mfrac><mi>t</mi><mn>365</mn></mfrac></msqrt></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\text{Range} = \text{Spot} \times \text{VIX} \times \sqrt{\frac{t}{365}}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 0.8778em; vertical-align: -0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">Range</span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.2778em;"></span><span class="mrel">=</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.2778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 0.8778em; vertical-align: -0.1944em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">Spot</span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.2222em;"></span><span class="mbin">×</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.2222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 0.7667em; vertical-align: -0.0833em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">VIX</span></span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.2222em;"></span><span class="mbin">×</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right: 0.2222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height: 2.44em; vertical-align: -0.8031em;"></span><span class="mord sqrt"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height: 1.6369em;"><span class="svg-align" style="top: -4.4em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height: 4.4em;"></span><span class="mord" style="padding-left: 1em;"><span class="mord"><span class="mopen nulldelimiter"></span><span class="mfrac"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height: 1.2921em;"><span style="top: -2.314em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height: 3em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord">365</span></span></span><span style="top: -3.23em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height: 3em;"></span><span class="frac-line" style="border-bottom-width: 0.04em;"></span></span><span style="top: -3.677em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height: 3em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal">t</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height: 0.686em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="mclose nulldelimiter"></span></span></span></span><span style="top: -3.5969em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height: 4.4em;"></span><span class="hide-tail" style="min-width: 1.02em; height: 2.48em;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="400em" height="2.48em" viewBox="0 0 400000 2592" preserveAspectRatio="xMinYMin slice"><path d="M424,2478
