<hr data-start="2015" data-end="2018">
<h2 data-section-id="1hk4w8e" data-start="2020" data-end="2078">📈 Step 3: Backtesting (THIS WILL IMPRESS YOUR MANAGER)</h2>
<p data-start="2080" data-end="2085">Take:</p>
<ul data-start="2086" data-end="2119">
<li data-section-id="1ybwk8k" data-start="2086" data-end="2100">
<p data-start="2088" data-end="2100">NIFTY data</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1sb0510" data-start="2101" data-end="2119">
<p data-start="2103" data-end="2119">India VIX data</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="2121" data-end="2126">Test:</p>
<ul data-start="2127" data-end="2192">
<li data-section-id="16md6t" data-start="2127" data-end="2162">
<p data-start="2129" data-end="2162">How often price stayed in range</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="boi1fl" data-start="2163" data-end="2192">
<p data-start="2165" data-end="2192">Profitability of strangle</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="2194" data-end="2225">👉 This converts your app from:</p>
<blockquote data-start="2226" data-end="2257">
<p data-start="2228" data-end="2257">“calculator” → <strong data-start="2243" data-end="2257">quant tool</strong></p>
</blockquote>
<hr data-start="2259" data-end="2262">
<h2 data-section-id="5o2ndm" data-start="2264" data-end="2296">💡 Step 4: Add Smart Features</h2>
<p data-start="2298" data-end="2320">You can level this up:</p>
<ul data-start="2322" data-end="2507">
<li data-section-id="13glsxv" data-start="2322" data-end="2364">
<p data-start="2324" data-end="2364">“Overpriced VIX” signal → sell options</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="19y735q" data-start="2365" data-end="2402">
<p data-start="2367" data-end="2402">“Underpriced VIX” → avoid selling</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ufdr94" data-start="2403" data-end="2444">
<p data-start="2405" data-end="2444">Range vs actual move comparison chart</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ik1gr5" data-start="2445" data-end="2507">
<p data-start="2447" data-end="2468">Daily recommendation:</p>
<ul data-start="2471" data-end="2507">
<li data-section-id="1sgz357" data-start="2471" data-end="2488">
<p data-start="2473" data-end="2488">“Sell strangle”</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="175ucjc" data-start="2491" data-end="2507">
<p data-start="2493" data-end="2507">“Avoid market”</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="2509" data-end="2512">
<h2 data-section-id="1i5pd2m" data-start="2514" data-end="2549">🔥 Big Reality Check (Important)</h2>
<p data-start="2551" data-end="2561">Your idea:</p>
<blockquote data-start="2562" data-end="2591">
<p data-start="2564" data-end="2591">“Full premium with no loss”</p>
</blockquote>
<p data-start="2593" data-end="2609">Let me be blunt:</p>
<ul data-start="2610" data-end="2696">
<li data-section-id="jomsep" data-start="2610" data-end="2645">
<p data-start="2612" data-end="2645">❌ No strategy gives <strong data-start="2632" data-end="2645">zero risk</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="bi5clt" data-start="2646" data-end="2696">
<p data-start="2648" data-end="2696">✔️ What you’re building = <strong data-start="2674" data-end="2696">probabilistic edge</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="2698" data-end="2729">This is how real traders think:</p>
<ul data-start="2730" data-end="2780">
<li data-section-id="gfk0i2" data-start="2730" data-end="2780">
<p data-start="2732" data-end="2780">“High probability, limited risk-adjusted return”</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="2782" data-end="2785">
<h2 data-section-id="6b9z3v" data-start="2787" data-end="2834">🧠 How You Can Present This (for internship)</h2>
<p data-start="2836" data-end="2855">Frame it like this:</p>
<blockquote data-start="2857" data-end="3026">
<p data-start="2859" data-end="3026">“Built a volatility-based predictive model using VIX to estimate daily trading ranges and tested its applicability in options selling strategies like short strangles.”</p>
</blockquote>
<p data-start="3028" data-end="3049">🔥 That sounds elite.</p>
