<p data-start="150" data-end="258">We’ll use <strong data-start="160" data-end="201"><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Streamlit</span></span></strong> because it’s the easiest way to turn Python into an app.</p>
<hr data-start="260" data-end="263">
<h1 data-section-id="18eitbk" data-start="265" data-end="309">🧱 PART 1: One-Time Setup (Do this slowly)</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="j3vt8s" data-start="311" data-end="338">✅ Step 1: Install Python</h2>
<ol data-start="339" data-end="494">
<li data-section-id="14udwfw" data-start="339" data-end="382">
<p data-start="342" data-end="382">Go to: <a data-start="349" data-end="382" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="decorated-link" href="https://www.python.org/downloads/">https://www.python.org/downloads/<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75]"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ftjksuqy.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="i8b69j" data-start="383" data-end="411">
<p data-start="386" data-end="411">Click <strong data-start="392" data-end="411">Download Python</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="120kmvb" data-start="412" data-end="430">
<p data-start="415" data-end="430">Run installer</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="ex73ob" data-start="431" data-end="477">
<p data-start="434" data-end="477">⚠️ IMPORTANT: Tick <strong data-start="453" data-end="477">“Add Python to PATH”</strong></p>
</li>
