<hr data-start="162" data-end="165">
<h1 data-section-id="1i1oas2" data-start="167" data-end="190">✅ Fix It Step-by-Step</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="mfo009" data-start="192" data-end="226">🔧 Step 1: Show File Extensions</h2>
<p data-start="228" data-end="274">Windows is hiding the real extension. Do this:</p>
<ol data-start="276" data-end="375">
<li data-section-id="drapu9" data-start="276" data-end="311">
<p data-start="279" data-end="311">Open your folder (<code data-start="297" data-end="310">VIXRangeApp</code>)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="134s7ib" data-start="312" data-end="340">
<p data-start="315" data-end="340">Click <strong data-start="321" data-end="329">View</strong> (top menu)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="j58sw7" data-start="341" data-end="375">
<p data-start="344" data-end="375">Tick <strong data-start="349" data-end="375">“File name extensions”</strong></p>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="377" data-end="409">👉 Now you’ll see the full name:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="410" data-end="428"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ftjksuqy.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none; max-height: 433px;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>app.py.txt</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="430" data-end="433">
<h2 data-section-id="hkxop6" data-start="435" data-end="464">🔧 Step 2: Rename Properly</h2>
<ol data-start="466" data-end="524">
