<hr data-start="283" data-end="286">
<h2 data-section-id="b62ngb" data-start="288" data-end="306">🧠 Simple Logic</h2>
<ul data-start="308" data-end="411">
<li data-section-id="1rz70ca" data-start="308" data-end="376">
<p data-start="310" data-end="376"><code data-start="310" data-end="333">pip install streamlit</code> → installs the software (one-time thing)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1507vzo" data-start="377" data-end="411">
<p data-start="379" data-end="411"><code data-start="379" data-end="387">app.py</code> → just your file name</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="413" data-end="422">Renaming:</p>
<blockquote data-start="423" data-end="514">
<p data-start="425" data-end="514">❌ does NOT delete Streamlit<br data-start="452" data-end="455">
❌ does NOT affect installation<br data-start="487" data-end="490">
✅ only fixes file type</p>
</blockquote>
<hr data-start="516" data-end="519">
<h2 data-section-id="o9fpzq" data-start="521" data-end="560">❗ Only reinstall IF this error comes</h2>
<p data-start="562" data-end="573">If you see:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="574" data-end="611"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ftjksuqy.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none; max-height: 433px;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>'streamlit' is not recognized</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="613" data-end="625">👉 THEN run:</p>
