I’ll walk you through it <strong data-start="98" data-end="125">very slowly and clearly</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="128" data-end="131">
<h1 data-section-id="ng8rbk" data-start="133" data-end="142">🎯 Goal</h1>
<p data-start="143" data-end="216">We want a terminal that is <strong data-start="170" data-end="216">already inside your folder (<code data-start="200" data-end="213">VIXRangeApp</code>)</strong></p>
<hr data-start="218" data-end="221">
<h1 data-section-id="7qm52h" data-start="223" data-end="255">✅ METHOD 1 (EASIEST — DO THIS)</h1>
<h2 data-section-id="1idlzrk" data-start="257" data-end="287">📂 Step 1: Open Your Folder</h2>
<ul data-start="288" data-end="336">
<li data-section-id="gakiyx" data-start="288" data-end="305">
<p data-start="290" data-end="305">Go to Desktop</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1oeyw3r" data-start="306" data-end="336">
<p data-start="308" data-end="336">Double-click <strong data-start="321" data-end="336">VIXRangeApp</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="338" data-end="341">
<h2 data-section-id="1t6o4lh" data-start="343" data-end="374">🧭 Step 2: Click Address Bar</h2>
<p data-start="376" data-end="435">At the top of the folder window, you’ll see something like:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="436" data-end="475"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ftjksuqy.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none; max-height: 433px;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>This PC &gt; Desktop &gt; VIXRangeApp</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="477" data-end="496">👉 Click on it once</p>
<p data-start="498" data-end="528">Now it becomes something like:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="529" data-end="574"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ftjksuqy.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none; max-height: 433px;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>C:\Users\YourName\Desktop\VIXRangeApp</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="576" data-end="579">
<h2 data-section-id="1vmp6q3" data-start="581" data-end="605"><span role="text">⌨️ Step 3: Type <code data-start="600" data-end="605">cmd</code></span></h2>
<p data-start="607" data-end="617">Just type:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="618" data-end="629"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-ftjksuqy.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none; max-height: 433px;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>cmd</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="631" data-end="650">and press <strong data-start="641" data-end="650">Enter</strong></p>
<hr data-start="652" data-end="655">
